snippet.textDisplay:
To all your skeptics, be reasonable. There are good reasons to be concerned and panicked. First, this is a new strain of Coronavirus that’s unresponsive to the vaccines on rotation by the pharma industry. Yes, I know they’re suspect. But, that means your immune system is self-deployed first if you do battle against this virus. And, you better hope and pray that you’ve got an effective system that can give much resistance. And, after the battle is fought, hopefully there is no permanent damage. To top it off, we’re unprepared for the enemy we can’t see. People are already dying, and this virus is non-discriminatory, so everything is fair game.

In addition, nothing is transparent and there’s poor coordination on how to contain this situation. Experts are scattered in their responses, and no one is sure how this thing came into existence. All we know is China, and that’s not helpful. We need investigations and deserve answers! Tell the truth!
